Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:53.57,Side Bar Bottom,text l,0000,0000,0000,,...وأخيرًا
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:24:00.50,Side Bar Top Bl,text r,0000,0000,0000,,فصل اغتيال الشوغن
